	* src/at91_misc.c (hal_clock_initialize): 
	* cdl/hal_arm_at91.cdl: Increase system clock (RTC) to run at 1MHz for
	better timing resolution.  CAUTION! this means that the system clock tick
	can never be more than 64ms.

